                    <div class="question">Do we need to have it all figured out yet?</div>
                    <div class="switchicon">
                        <img src="https://assets-global.website-files.com/611678a38604517d3bd8ef0c/611e7a63bb7311d2d8ea2b32_close.svg" loading="lazy" alt="" class="closeicon"/>
                        <img src="https://assets-global.website-files.com/611678a38604517d3bd8ef0c/611e7a46aac87d1d13e1c3a2_open.svg" loading="lazy" alt="" class="openicon"/>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="answer">
                    <p class="faqparagraph">
                        Certainly not, but we need to be confident that you have a committed and agile team with a suitable starting point and the tenacity and ability to iterate and learn. You will receive input during the 8-week accelerator to help you grow and achieve your goals. We are interested in why you are the right team to support and invest in.
