                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="answer">
                    <p class="faqparagraph">The ideal combination is a business lead (i.e. a team member with a strategic focus and decision-making ability) and a technical lead (i.e. an operational, hands-on team member responsible for implementing your service).</p>
