                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="answer">
                    <p class="faqparagraph">Apart from the time commitment explained above, you will require a computer with internet access and sufficient data to attend all virtual sessions on a conference tool such as Zoom. Ideally, your connection and data will allow you to attend the sessions with your video on.</p>
                    <p class="faqparagraph"></p>
                    <p class="faqparagraph"></p>
                    <p class="faqparagraph"></p>
                    <p class="faqparagraph"></p>
                    <p class="faqparagraph"></p>
