            <div class="faq">
                <div data-w-id="97ba8b78-ee68-d24c-bc6e-9ce9c757302b" class="faq-header">
                    <div class="question">What is a Business Service Provider (BSP)?</div>
                    <div class="switchicon">
                        <img src="https://assets-global.website-files.com/611678a38604517d3bd8ef0c/611e7a63bb7311d2d8ea2b32_close.svg" loading="lazy" alt="" class="closeicon"/>
                        <img src="https://assets-global.website-files.com/611678a38604517d3bd8ef0c/611e7a46aac87d1d13e1c3a2_open.svg" loading="lazy" alt="" class="openicon"/>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="answer">
                    <p class="faqparagraph">Business Service Providers (BSPs) are third-party solution providers with expertise in the WhatsApp Business API. BSPs, like Turn.io, can help you communicate with your customers on WhatsApp for the approved use cases of customer support and time-sensitive, personalized notifications.</p>
                    <p class="faqparagraph"></p>
                    <p class="faqparagraph"></p>
                    <p class="faqparagraph"></p>
                    <p class="faqparagraph"></p>
                    <p class="faqparagraph"></p>
                    <p class="faqparagraph"></p>
                    <p class="faqparagraph"></p>
                    <p class="faqparagraph"></p>
                    <p class="faqparagraph last"></p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq">
                <div data-w-id="97ba8b78-ee68-d24c-bc6e-9ce9c757302b" class="faq-header">
                    <div class="question">Do we need to use Turn.io as a BSP?</div>
                    <div class="switchicon">
                        <img src="https://assets-global.website-files.com/611678a38604517d3bd8ef0c/611e7a63bb7311d2d8ea2b32_close.svg" loading="lazy" alt="" class="closeicon"/>
                        <img src="https://assets-global.website-files.com/611678a38604517d3bd8ef0c/611e7a46aac87d1d13e1c3a2_open.svg" loading="lazy" alt="" class="openicon"/>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="answer">
                    <p class="faqparagraph">Turn.io is hosting the Chat for GenAI Accelerator, and you will receive a Turn License for the duration of the Accelerator. All hands-on sessions and the building of your chatbot will be on the Turn.io platform. For this purpose, you must use Turn.io as your Business Solution Provider (BSP) after the Accelerator.</p>
                    <p class="faqparagraph"></p>
                    <p class="faqparagraph"></p>
                    <p class="faqparagraph"></p>
