                    <p class="faqparagraph"></p>
                    <p class="faqparagraph"></p>
                    <p class="faqparagraph"></p>
                    <p class="faqparagraph last"></p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq">
                <div data-w-id="97ba8b78-ee68-d24c-bc6e-9ce9c757302b" class="faq-header">
                    <div class="question">What is the WhatsApp Business API, and why select it as the means of communication?</div>
                    <div class="switchicon">
                        <img src="https://assets-global.website-files.com/611678a38604517d3bd8ef0c/611e7a63bb7311d2d8ea2b32_close.svg" loading="lazy" alt="" class="closeicon"/>
                        <img src="https://assets-global.website-files.com/611678a38604517d3bd8ef0c/611e7a46aac87d1d13e1c3a2_open.svg" loading="lazy" alt="" class="openicon"/>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="answer">
                    <p class="faqparagraph">
                        The WhatsApp Business API powers communication with users worldwide so that you can connect with them on WhatsApp in a simple, secure, and reliable way.
                        <br/>
                        <br/>
                        The WhatsApp Business API is a paid product. However, as part of the Accelerator, you will be granted a subsidized license for up to 6 months; further use of the API may result in monthly fees and/or messaging fees.
                        <br/>
